---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { useTranslations } from '../i18n/utils';

const t = useTranslations('en');
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Kunga DEMPA TSANG">
  <!-- Hero Section with Parallax Effect -->
  <section class="relative h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513364776144-60967b0f800f?w=1600&q=80'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in">
        Kunga DEMPA TSANG
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl opacity-90 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Exploring liminal spaces between reality and imagination
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Artist Statement - Full Width with Image -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460661419201-fd4cecdf8a8b?w=800&q=80" 
            alt="Artistic workspace"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl w-full h-[500px] object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
            Artist Statement
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="italic border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
              Dans mes tableaux, ce que j'ai cherché à peindre, ce sont ces moments suspendus du quotidien, quand la solitude et la contemplation se mêlent.
            </p>
            <p>
              Je me suis inspirée des espaces liminaux, ces lieux entre le réel et l'imaginaire. J'ai essayé de les traduire dans mes peintures à travers la lumière, les textures et les superpositions.
            </p>
            <p>
              Mon envie, c'est aussi de créer des espaces où chacun peut se perdre, se réinventer, et interroger son rapport au temps et à l'espace.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              En ce moment, je fais pas mal de petits dessins au pastel sec. C'est plus doux que mes peintures et ça me permet aussi d'aborder ces thèmes autrement.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Biography Section - Asymmetric Layout -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <!-- Left Column - Bio Text -->
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
              Biography
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Kunga Dempa Tsang is a contemporary painter based in Paris. Born in <strong>Markham, Tibet</strong>, her journey led her through India before settling in France, where she has developed her distinctive artistic voice.
              </p>
              <p>
                In 2018, she began her artistic studies at <strong>Prép'art</strong> in Paris, then continued her education at the <strong>École Supérieure d'Art de Clermont Métropole</strong>, where she obtained her <strong>DNSEP in June 2024</strong>, with honors from the jury.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Her work explores the boundaries between the tangible and the imaginary, creating atmospheric spaces that invite contemplation and introspection.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Column - Info Cards -->
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-2">Origin</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Markham, Tibet</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-2">Education</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-900 font-medium">DNSEP</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">École Supérieure d'Art</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Clermont Métropole, 2024</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-2">Based in</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Paris, France</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">18th Arrondissement</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-2">Contact</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-900 text-sm">+33 6 63 16 37 69</p>
              <p class="text-gray-900 text-sm">dempatsang@gmail.com</p>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/kunga.dempa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline text-sm block mt-2">
                @kunga.dempa
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Exhibitions Section - Timeline Style -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16 text-center text-gray-900">
          Exhibitions
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <!-- Exhibition 1 -->
          <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-primary">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
              <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-primary text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">
                2025
              </span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Double Trouble</h3>
              <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-2">ART EMERGENCE EXPOSITION</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">September 17 - November 2, 2025</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Organized by ARTAGON</p>
              <a 
                href="https://www.artagon.org/art-emergence-exposition/" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:underline font-medium"
              >
                View Exhibition
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Exhibition 2 -->
          <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-gray-300">
            <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
              <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-gray-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">
                2023
              </span>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Ephemeral Space Exhibition</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Organized in collaboration with Sœur Tokyo</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Paris, France</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action - Full Width with Gradient -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Interested in my work?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Available for commissions, exhibitions, and collaborations.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a 
          href="/contact/" 
          class="px-10 py-4 bg-white text-gray-900 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
        >
          Get in Touch
        </a>
        <a 
          href="/gallery/" 
          class="px-10 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-md hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors font-semibold text-lg inline-block"
        >
          View Gallery
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 1s ease-out;
  }
</style>

